name: Drank After Work #07 // Never Give Up
description: A friend of mine was one of the best artists in our group. But he couldn't find a job and gave up on art and started to drive trucks in a warehouse. He kept drinking and smoking the whole day even while driving the forklifts. One day he finally realized he was in a black hole, and he decided he had to change and get back to his art. Never give up. Drank
